snippet.title: Overstorm - Unreleased Game for GBA
snippet.description:
A prototype of the unreleased Overstorm for the Nintendo Game Boy Advance, created by Quantized Bit. Overstorm is a side-scrolling platformer that doesn't seem to have progressed past an alpha build created for demonstration at "Games Convention 2003". However, in 2014, the developers decided to give away an alpha build of the game, featuring five different levels, in a Indiestand game sale of their last product, Volt: Battery on the Loose.

More Info: hiddenpalace.org   /Overstorm_(Prototype)
